  "title": "Sales Course Consultant (Travelling Opportunities)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Engage with prospective students to understand their educational needs and goals</li><li>Provide detailed information about the courses, curriculum, and learning outcomes</li><li>Conduct personalized consultations to assess students' backgrounds, interests, and learning preferences</li><li>Recommend suitable courses and learning pathways based on students' objectives and career aspirations</li><li>Collaborate with the sales and marketing teams to optimize lead generation strategies and conversion rates</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>No prior experience are required, coaching provided</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team</li><li>Passion for sales and building relationships with customers</li><li>Proactive attitude and ability to adapt to changing situations</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Vibrant company culture with opportunities for growth and advancement</li><li>Comprehensive training and ongoing support</li><li>Fun and dynamic work environment</li></ul>",
